data.description: NO MORE SHOWING  Good condition, .   Eat-in kitchen boasts plenty of counter space granite countertops  recently replaced stainless steel, appliances, Splash Back .   Spacious dining room opens up to the expansive living room with a sliding door out to the back yard. This floor also features a convenient powder room. Upstairs you will find a large master bedroom with street views . The other two bedrooms on this floor are also nicely sized . In the lower level you will find the a  multifunctional recreation room, another full bath, and an ample utility room. The desirable Point of Woods neighborhood is part of a vibrant community which is centrally located inside the city of Manassas just minutes from local shops, supermarkets,  entertainment, and restaurants.
